FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://localhost:5000

# Simple Books API
API quản lý sách đơn giản với thiết kế theo phong cách API Blueprint.

# Group Books
Các thao tác liên quan đến kho sách.

## Books Collection [/books]

### List all books [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Book])

### Create a new book [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (NewBook)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Book)

## Book Details [/books/{id}]
+ Parameters
    + id: `1` (string, required) - ID duy nhất của cuốn sách.

### Get a book by ID [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Book)

+ Response 404 (application/json)
    + Body
            {
                "error": "Book not found"
            }

### Update a book [PUT]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (NewBook)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Book)

+ Response 404 (application/json)
    + Body
            {
                "error": "Book not found"
            }

### Delete a book [DELETE]
+ Response 204

+ Response 404 (application/json)
    + Body
            {
                "error": "Book not found"
            }

# Data Structures

## Book (object)
+ id: `1` (string, required)
+ title: `Clean Code` (string, required)
+ author: `Robert C. Martin` (string, required)
+ publishedYear: 2008 (number, required)
+ genre: `Software Engineering` (string, optional)

## NewBook (object)
+ title: `Clean Code` (string, required)
+ author: `Robert C. Martin` (string, required)
+ publishedYear: 2008 (number, required)
+ genre: `Software Engineering` (string, optional)
